abiword
------------------------------------------
AbiWord is a powerful, free and cross platform word processing program 
similar to Microsoft Word. It is suitable for almost all word processing 
tasks.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.7-1
  libatk1.0_0-1.30.0-1
  libcairo2-1.8.10-2
  libenchant1-1.6.0-1
  libfontconfig1-2.8.0-1
  libfribidi0-0.19.2-1
  libgcc1-4.5.0-1
  libgdk_pixbuf2.0_0-2.20.1-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.24.1-1
  libgoffice0.8_8-0.8.10-1
  libgsf1_114-1.14.18-1
  libgtk2.0_0-2.20.1-1
  libjpeg8-8b-1
  libpango1.0_0-1.28.1-2
  libpng14-1.4.3-2
  librsvg2_2-2.26.3-1
  libstdc++6-4.5.0-1
  libwv1.2_4-1.2.7-1
  libX11_6-1.3.5-1
  libxml2-2.7.7-1
  zlib0-1.2.5-1
(abiword-plugins)
  gnome-utils-2.28.2-1
  libAiksaurusGTK1.2_0-1.2.1-10
  libgtkmathview0-0.8.0-10
  liblink-grammar4-4.6.7-1
  libots1_0-0.5.0-10
  libpsiconv6-0.9.8-10
  libreadline7-6.0.3-2
  libtidy0_99_0-20090325-1
  libwmf027-0.2.8.4-10
  libwpd0.8_8-0.8.14-10
  libwpg0.1_1-0.1.3-10
